id":"9f685f1c4439b2ccc33c7fb08abe9798054829b0","tid":1055684,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bcf70e0e23060f89194a70ff1890ecb185ca552e","tid":1055684,"uid":52459,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T23:56:41.000Z","msg":"香港轉工要好，都係入政苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T00:20:20.000Z","msg":"入政府搵得幾多呀？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T00:50:59.000Z","msg":"只要你迎合到個工作環境<br />\n至少唔駛怕會唔會被裁<br />\n人工有無得加<br />\n<br />\n只係呢兩點 今時今日已經係好好"},{"pid":"4d09fbbb0e5445f6cf31f8052ab88426e501eed4","tid":1055684,"uid":119330,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bdf29298019c4fb3dea5d7117ae0bef4f588c495","tid":1055684,"uid":18385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T00:30:24.000Z","msg":"香港行前好多，日本依家先發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T00:54:49.000Z","msg":"其實日本好早就已經改變左終身聘用制<br />\n但問題係當年靠終身聘用制上位果班<br />\n仲係中高層度話事<br />\n職場文化呢樣野 唔係可以立刻可以改變<br />\n所以就算日本新一代已經轉變<br />\n無奈好多大公司 話事果班 都係信奉終身聘用制<br />\n<br />\n不過咁多年過去<br />\n果班中高層都走得差不多<br />\n再加上日本勞動人口減少<br />\n外國人多左去日本工作<br />\n所以加速推動職場文化改變"},{"pid":"ff80721d07e857b3a07f04c055ba5095ca47b026","tid":1055684,"uid":91146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T00:56:12.000Z","msg":"大把人有1000 萬日元一年啦"},{"pid":"f071e04eeb255e2628417b4b9f1ed36bd01107fa","tid":1055684,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T01:05:12.000Z","msg":"香港弊在多contract制剝削員工呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27387b3e5fc5b6ae63c65b93e6adaeb4362288f9","tid":1055684,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7736090d9e4a09556fdf8a8878c6d001a79b7938","tid":1055684,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score